<!-- 技术原理 -->
<section id="tech-principle" class="py-20 bg-white">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="inline-block text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">核心技术原理</h2>
<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
<p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">我们的动力电池梯次利用解决方案基于先进的电化学修复技术与智能电池管理系统，实现电池全生命周期的价值最大化</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
<div>
<h3 class="section-title text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">电池梯次利用流程</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">动力电池梯次利用是指对新能源汽车退役电池进行回收与再利用的过程。通过专业的检测、分选、修复技术，使退役电池在储能等领域获得"第二次生命"。</p>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-start">
<div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">1</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">电池回收与拆解</h4>
<p class="text-gray-600">通过专业渠道回收退役动力电池，经过安全拆解，分离出电池模组与电芯</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start">
<div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">2</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">性能检测与分选</h4>
<p class="text-gray-600">采用高精度检测设备，对电池容量、内阻等参数进行全面检测，并根据性能进行分级</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start">
<div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">3</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">电池修复与再生</h4>
<p class="text-gray-600">通过专利电化学修复技术，激活电池活性物质，恢复电池容量，延长使用寿命</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start">
<div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">4</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">重组与系统集成</h4>
<p class="text-gray-600">根据应用需求，将修复后的电池模组重新组合，配置智能BMS系统，形成完整储能系统</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start">
<div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">5</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">应用与监控</h4>
<p class="text-gray-600">在储能、备用电源等领域实现应用，并通过云平台进行全生命周期监控与管理</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
<img src="https://public.readdy.ai/ai/img_res/be09c377e4102c599a0727f2e606d5be.jpg" alt="电池梯次利用流程图" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top">
</div>
